      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "---\n**Setup Instructions:** After importing all dashboards, replace the placeholder IDs in the markdown links above:\n- `SERVICE_HEALTH_DASHBOARD_ID` - ID from Service Health dashboard\n- `RESOURCE_HEALTH_DASHBOARD_ID` - ID from Resource Health dashboard\n- `RECOMMENDATIONS_DASHBOARD_ID` - ID from Recommendations dashboard\n- `SECURITY_DASHBOARD_ID` - ID from Security dashboard\n\nFind the dashboard ID in the URL when viewing each dashboard: `.../#dashboard;id=<THIS_VALUE>`"
    }
